Introduction

Park Yeeun is a South Korean trainee under High Up Entertainment. She is a member of the agency's upcoming girl group.

From April to May 2024, Park Yeeun was a contestant on Mnet's survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she was eliminated in episode 7. At that time, she was a trainee under WAKEONE.
